@startuml ruoccofabrizio_azure-open-ai-embeddings-qna

actor User
participant "Streamlit Web App" as WebApp
participant "Azure OpenAI Service" as AzureOpenAI
participant "Vector Store" as VectorStore
participant "GPT-3" as GPT3
queue "Azure Queue" as Queue
participant "BatchStartProcessing\nAzure Function" as BatchStart
participant "BatchPushResults\nAzure Function" as BatchPush
database "Azure Blob Storage" as BlobStorage

User -> WebApp: Ask question
WebApp -> AzureOpenAI: Create query embedding
AzureOpenAI --> WebApp: Return embedding
WebApp -> VectorStore: Search similar documents
VectorStore --> WebApp: Return relevant chunks
WebApp -> GPT3: Generate answer (query + chunks)
GPT3 --> WebApp: Return generated answer
WebApp --> User: Display answer

User -> BatchStart: Trigger batch processing
activate BatchStart
BatchStart -> Queue: Add processing messages
deactivate BatchStart

Queue -> BatchPush: Trigger document processing
activate BatchPush
BatchPush -> BlobStorage: Read document
BlobStorage --> BatchPush: Return document content
BatchPush -> AzureOpenAI: Create document embedding
AzureOpenAI --> BatchPush: Return embedding
BatchPush -> VectorStore: Store document embedding
deactivate BatchPush

@enduml